Package edu.stanford.cfuller.imageanalysistools.clustering

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Positioned
    Describes something that has a 3D position that can calculate its distance to some other object with a 3D position.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cluster
    A representation of a single Cluster of ClusterObject that might result from applying a clustering algorithm to a collection of objects.
    ClusterObject
    Representation of an Object identified in an image with some defined spatial position that can be clustered.
    DEGaussianMixtureModelClustering
    Implements Gaussian mixture model clustering for a set of ClusterObjects using a differential evolution algorithm for the likelihood maximization.
    GaussianLikelihoodObjectiveFunction
    A function that calculates the likelihood of observing a set of points given a set of Gaussian sources generating them.
    ObjectClustering
    Utilites for doing clustering of objects in an Image.
